### Find all users as admin
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter active users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users?page=0&size=20&status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter admin users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users?page=0&size=20&role=ADMIN
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Search by keyword
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users?page=0&size=20&keyword=john
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

